data.description: Nestled In The Heart Of Perkins, This Charming Ranch-style Home Offers A Perfect Blend Of Comfort And Style. As You Step Inside, You'll Immediately Notice The Thoughtful Updates That Have Been Made To Enhance The Interior. The Detail Has Been Carefully Considered To Create A Welcoming Atmosphere.the Bathroom Is A Standout Feature, Boasting Ceramic Tile Flooring And Surround, Adding A Touch Of Luxury To Your Daily Routine. Wood Laminate Plank Flooring Throughout The Home Not Only Exudes Beauty But Also Ensures Easy Maintenance For Busy Homeowners.the Heart Of The Home Is The Spacious Kitchen, Which Has Been Beautifully Refreshed. Additionally, There's Ample Space For A Private Office And A Great Fenced In Back Yard For Outdoor Enjoyment. Newer Roof & Low Maintaince Vinyl Siding. Don't Miss The Opportunity To Make This Home Yours. It's The Perfect Blend Of Modern Living And Timeless Charm!
